    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nお願いした件はどうなってますか？",
      "startTime": 3.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、歌う曲を急に変更するのは難しいですよね",
      "startTime": 7.4082084974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そうした方がいいと思うんです\n今の私じゃ、周りの期待に応えられないから……",
      "startTime": 16.9999990781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そのことだが、昨日話した後ずっと考えていたんだ\n麻奈ならこんな時、なんて言うだろうって……",
      "startTime": 26.9565985046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんなら……？",
      "startTime": 30.6565985046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、麻奈ならこう言うんじゃないかな",
      "startTime": 32.4906347516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "「超えたとか超えないとか、周りの声に踊らされないで\n歌を届けたい人のことを思いながら歌えばいいんだよ」",
      "startTime": 40.9573011639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "届けたい人のことを思いながら歌えばいい……",
      "startTime": 45.6239670676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "「もっと自分に自信を持って。さくらちゃんは\n天才の私が見込んだアイドルなんだから」",
      "startTime": 53.111610405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そして麻奈は笑って言うんだ\n「でも私だって負けないからねー」",
      "startTime": 59.4449381433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "負けないからねー、って……なんですかそれ\n全然緊張感ないじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 66.4999942461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、どうしてだろう。ちゃんと話したことはないのに\n麻奈さんならそう言いそうな気がします",
      "startTime": 75.1999978064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "きっと麻奈さんも\n届けたい人のことを思いながら歌ってたんですね",
      "startTime": 79.9999957719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "負けたくない気持ちも楽しんで\nみんなに笑顔を届けてたんですね",
      "startTime": 87.5333270707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "……ふう",
      "startTime": 91.9333373068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり麻奈さんは凄いなぁ……",
      "startTime": 93.4441851698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "さくらだって同じだろ？\n麻奈と比べるために歌っていた訳じゃないはずだ",
      "startTime": 99.8753865166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね。私は届けたい人のことを思いながら\n歌えばいいんですよね",
      "startTime": 108.6666578608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "届けたい人のことを思いながら……\n私が歌を届けたい人は……",
      "startTime": 115.6999891596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n昨日言ったことは取り消します。前言撤回です！",
      "startTime": 120.3999876337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり私、麻奈さんの曲を歌いたいです！\n私に歌わせて下さい！",
      "startTime": 128.6999876337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。想いのこもった\nさくららしい歌を楽しみにしているぞ",
      "startTime": 133.9596220577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――祭典当日",
      "startTime": 138.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ出番だ。準備はいいか？",
      "startTime": 140.3596057818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　私らしく心を込めて精一杯歌ってきます！",
      "startTime": 143.7596006955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いい笑顔だ。もう迷いはないようだな",
      "startTime": 149.589593721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "……この前、琴乃ちゃんと話したんです",
      "startTime": 153.7895927037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは「月ストはサニピに負けない\nパフォーマンスをするから」って言ってくれました",
      "startTime": 160.0999571162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "それを聞いて、私も負けないくらい\n凄いステージにしなきゃなって思ったんです",
      "startTime": 166.7332904496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "私が競うべき相手は麻奈さんじゃない……\nもっと近くに最高のライバルがいたんです",
      "startTime": 174.2999489782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "憧れの麻奈さんを追いかけて、ライバルの月ストと\n競い合って、サニピはもっともっと強くなりますよ～！",
      "startTime": 181.8332823115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……\nさくらの成長を、俺も麻奈も楽しみにしているぞ",
      "startTime": 188.8917389799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr022.m4a",
      "text": "はい、見ていて下さい！\nこれからも元気一杯輝きます！",
      "startTime": 196.0999499955,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
